wiki.summary: MUSIC | After releasing the acclaimed video for the track "Try", Pink has just released her new music video. The single chosen was "Just Give Me a Reason", part of the CD "The Truth About Love." With the participation of the singer of the American band fun., Nate Ruess, which also shares some scenes with the singer, the clip is composed of images of a couple who enters into crisis, and as well as describing the lyrics, questions remain about the what happened to the love between them.
